nodes.text: In 26 ABY, the Khommite Jedi Knight Dorsk 82 utilized a starship in an effort to rescue a number of droids from the planet Ando during the Yuuzhan Vong War. Along with his pilot, Hhen, Dorsk 82 tried to get thirty-eight droids off-planet ahead of a mob of Aqualish intent on destroying them to appease the Yuuzhan Vong. The ship was destroyed on the order of a security officer, killing Hhen and destroying the droids on board.
